msgstr "Dokumentace"

#: applications/luci-app-privoxy/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/privoxy/privoxy.js:269
#: applications/luci-app-privoxy/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/privoxy/privoxy.js:272
